data.description: This is the home you've been dreaming about!  You won't beleive the updated interior; from the moment you walk through the front door & see the vaulted ceiling, to the luxury vinyl flooring which is ideal for kids & pets to the custom updated wood burning fireplace surround.  Kitchen is open with SS appliances newer KitchenAid dishwasher & electric range, to a custom island with butcher block top & granite counters.  Step out to your back deck for casual entertaining.  If you love shiplap, then you'll love this house.  Custom millwork abounds in this house from the walls to new baseboards.  The primary suite is spacious with custom millwork and completely updated bath in the last 3 years.  Two other bedrooms are currently being used as an office & child's playroom.   The guest bath has been updated as well.  The lower level is waiting for your design & creativity as you walk out to your spacious fenced in back yard.  Close to highways & shopping.
